I notified the same behaviour.
BooleanQuery ignores its own boost factor during calculation. You can =
set
it, but
this will not change anything. If you want to change the boost of a =
boolean
query,
you have to set it for every clause (term). Sorry.
Maybe this could be changed in the further.
Regard,
